Normal structure
if condition:
elif condition:
else:

short hand

if condition: statement
if a > b: print("a is greater than b")

statement if condition else statement
print("A") if a > b else print("B")

Operator
and
or

Nested
x = 41
if x > 10:
  print("Above ten,")
  if x > 20:
    print("and also above 20!")
  else:
    print("but not above 20.")
